px;\">history</td><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">Returns the History object for the window.<br>See also The History Object.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">innerHeight</td><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">Returns the height of the window\'s content area (viewport) including scrollbars</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">innerWidth</td><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">Returns the width of a window\'s content area (viewport) including scrollbars</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">length</td><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">Returns the number of &lt;iframe&gt; elements in the current window</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">localStorage</td><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">Allows to save key/value pairs in a web browser. Stores the data with no expiration date</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">location</td><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">Returns the Location object for the window.<br>See also the The Location Object.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);padding:7px 15px;\">name</td><td style=\"border-color:var(--post-constructor-redactor-table-border-color,#eeeff1);paddin